{"tid":1071154,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《熱血合唱團》劉德華演音樂老師感化學生　《五個小孩的校長》編導再度關注本地教育","createTime":"2019-03-21T06:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T05:00:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"b5d94ebb504643d63a0a824fb5144cc8a6f60550","tid":1071154,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:56:54.000Z","msg":"劉德華化身暖男中學老師。在《五個小孩的校長》導演關信輝新作《熱血合唱團》，劉德華飾演的音樂指揮家，去到Band 3中學，誓要令社會眼中的「廢青」，重拾理想和熱誠，題材勵志，劉德華亦跟戲中一班年青演員如王智騫、林愷鈴等新人擦出火花。<br />\n劉德華在《熱血合唱團》演美國著名華籍指揮家，有音樂界鐵血教官之稱的嚴梓朗，在音樂界淡出一段日子後，應邀出任香港一個「熱血合唱團試驗計劃」，當中學員主要來自三間 Band 3學校的學生，這批學生組成古典音樂合唱團，須接受特訓9個月後參加「校際合唱團比賽」。<br />\n嚴sir在跟各學生相處中，了解到每張臉背後都總有故事，每隊合唱團都總有他們合奏出的生命樂曲。這33名中學廢青遇上帶著一個不可告人秘密的鐵面教官，經歷汗水與淚水，在生命影響生命下，他們的樂曲又會是怎樣？<br />\n在《熱血合唱團》的預告中，劉德華重新演繹經典歌曲《獅子山下》，伴隨一幕幕「熱血合唱團」成員成長及奮鬥的感人場面，包括充滿歡笑與淚水的訓練過程。當中劉德華於戲中有不少哽咽場面，更與合唱團成員相擁而哭，到底經歷重重困難的指揮家「嚴 Sir」與合唱團成員最終能否得到觀眾的掌聲？<br />\n《熱血合唱團》有不少觀眾熟悉的面孔，劉德華以外並有盧冠廷、雷頌德、謝君豪、尹揚明、李麗珍等演出，而有「最美星二代」之稱的龔慈恩女兒林愷鈴，亦首次演出電影飾其中一名Band 3學生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2300000/2303041/andy_thumb_20190321_p_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2300000%2F2303041%2Fandy_thumb_20190321_p_1024.jpg&h=1b50413e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2300000/2303041/andylayu6_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2300000%2F2303041%2Fandylayu6_1024.jpg&h=ef1e00b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2300000/2303041/andylayu10_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2300000%2F2303041%2Fandylayu10_1024.jpg&h=5cf23ddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oY3juPfi92Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoY3juPfi92Y&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3PzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=04211997\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oY3juPfi92Y</a>"},{"pid":"74e0d8a37d909b35dcd005d8a6fceff251211eee","tid":1071154,"uid":124277,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:07:43.000Z","msg":"劉德華, 飾演一個熱愛扮劉德華的音樂家"},{"pid":"c87ddaa170ef158f4e352b62fa1202abe3287b94","tid":1071154,"uid":10338,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:11:23.000Z","msg":"教細路唱中國人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46358b63866f9b9bbe6eea1a4d5738783472e31","tid":1071154,"uid":15558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"74e0d8a37d909b35dcd005d8a6fceff251211eee","tid":1071154,"uid":124277,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:07:43.000Z","msg":"劉德華, 飾演一個熱愛扮劉德華的音樂家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7686807f699bf18d7e03e6161fc816943f1503bf","tid":1071154,"uid":149494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:54:19.000Z","msg":"做中學老師都要set到個頭劉華咁<br />\n辛苦哂呢個阿sir"},{"pid":"29f4a124b53878126c9b58497b17135dad35b8e0","tid":1071154,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:56:08.000Z","msg":"又唱獅子山下 悶唔悶啲"},{"pid":"b29378aa2470bdacce398